title: HNK-Fight
info:
This is part of a group of modules called from the author "Area 05:  Hokuto No Ken".

"This area is *!*  recommended  *!* to all those people KenShiro's fanatic. (Hokuto No Ken also called NorthStar)
These modules below are quite small because they were composed for a videogame. (never realized...)
Therefore some instruments could not have a great audio quality ...but this is balanced from the high quality of remixes!

HNK-Fight: Fight!Fight! During duels...Great remix!"
